r, rash, itching, anorexia, nausea, vomiting, fatigue, malaise, right upper quadrant pain, dark urine, pale stools, and jaundice. Periodic monitoring of hepatic function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Rufinamide, Paramethadione, More', 'Naloxone, Nalmefene, Dexfenfluramine, Ephedrine, Lorcaserin, Diethylpropion, Mazindol', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/89257/', '[1] "Product Information. ReVia (naltrexone)." DuPont Pharmaceuticals, Wilmington, DE.', 1767369485);
